commit.message:
Update for latest versions of dependencies

- Egoboo was updated for the latest version of Idlib and Idlib: Game
Engine. A lot of functionality which was part of Egoboo is now
provided by these dependencies (in particular w.r.t. the build
system and math).
- The build system was updated and the
project structure was improved.
- Formatting was fixed.

commit.message: Update buildsystem/ci, update for latest version of dependencies

Resolve cyclic dependencies problems

Egoboo and Egolib had cyclic includes. These were removed by
moving all source code (except of a sole main function)
from Egoboo into Egolib.
Update buildsystem/ci

Update for latest versions of dependencies

Egoboo was updated for the latest version of Idlib and Idlib: Game
Engine.
Remove dead code
fs: Remove platform-specific 'fs_fileExists'
fs: Remove platform-specific 'fs_copyFile'

Update for latest versions of dependencies

Egoboo was updated for the latest version of Idlib and Idlib: Game
Engine.
fs: Remove dead code
fs: Remove platform-specific 'fs_createDirectory'
fs: Rewrite 'fs_removeDirectoryAndContents'
fs: Remove platform-specific 'fs_removeDirectory'
fs: Remove platform-specific 'fs_deleteFile'
fs: Remove platform-specific 'fs_fileIsDirectory'

fs: Remove redundant parameter

Every call to 'fs_removeDirectoryAndContents' passes 'VFS_TRUE' as the argument to parameter 'recursive'. Consequently, that parameter can be removed.

vfs: Remove redundant parameter

Every call to 'vfs_removeDirectoryAndContents' passes 'VFS_TRUE' as the
argument to parameter 'recursive'. Consequently, that parameter can be
removed.

Update for latest versions of dependencies

Egoboo was updated for the latest version of Idlib and Idlib: Game Engine.
Add submodule idlib-game-engine

Update buildsystem/ci

Update for Visual Studio Community 2017 15.5.0.
In all Visual Studio project files:
- C++ version is C++ 17
- Enforce type conversion rules is enabled
- Runtime type support is enabled
- OpenMP support is disabled
- Remove references to non-existing projects

Fixes

- Switch from integer math to floating-point math in editor.
- Proper initialization of camera system in game.
